{"word":"σχέσις","slug":"σχέσις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n101841\" key=\"sxe/sis\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σχέσις</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">εως</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἔχω, σχεῖν</etym>) <sense id=\"n101841.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">state, condition</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ς. τοῦ σώματος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">habit</tr_> of body, much <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">like</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">διάθεσις</ref></xr>, which is alterable, opp. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἕξις</foreign> (constitution or temperament, which is permanent), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg010.perseus-grc1:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Art.\">Art.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8</biblScope> </bibl>; hence <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐν σχέσει</foreign>, of <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">temporary, passing conditions</tr_>, opp. those which have become constitutional (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐν ἕξει</etym>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.533</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τί διαφέρει ς. ἕξεως</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg015:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Luc.\">Luc.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S